'''警犬'''是為[[警察|警察]]機構服務的[[工作犬|工作犬]]，在[[西方世界|西方世界]]時被喚作'''K-9'''（英語'''canine'''的[[同音異義語|同音異義語]]詞）。最常用的品種為[[德國牧羊犬|德國牧羊犬]]，近年[[比利時瑪連萊犬|比利時瑪連萊犬]]亦開始被廣泛使用。蓄意傷害或殺害警犬在很多國家已經被列為嚴重的刑事罪行<ref name=slate>{{cite news|publisher=Slate|last=Palmer|first=Brian|title=So Help You, Dog - How does a canine cop become a "sworn officer"|date=2008-07-18|url=http://www.slate.com/id/2195529/|accessdate=2013-04-24|archive-date=2011-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605215232/http://www.slate.com/id/2195529/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，刑罰比一般[[虐待動物|虐待動物]]為重，甚至等同或接近襲警的罪行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.policek9.com/html/statutes.html|publisher=Police K9|title=Statutes protecting Police Dogs|accessdate=2013-04-24|archive-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116060337/http://www.policek9.com/html/statutes.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>各地的執法部門越來越多為其警犬穿上[[防彈衣|防彈衣]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Protecting Police K-9s with ballistic vests|publisher=Police Dog Protection|url=http://vestnpdp.com/index.html|access-date=2013-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130906215249/http://www.vestnpdp.com/index.html|archive-date=2013-09-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|publisher=The Mississippi Press|title=Police dog receives new bulletproof vest|date=2008-07-24|last=Wright|first=Ryan|url=http://www.gulflive.com/news/mississippipress/index.ssf?/base/news/1216894503312760.xml}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>及配戴[[徽章|徽章]]<ref name=slate/><ref>{{cite news|publisher=Decatur Daily|title=Decatur's first police dog buried with his badge at training center|last=Huggins|first=Paul|date=2007-08-03|url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-32530168_ITM|accessdate=2013-04-24|archive-date=2013-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015124707/http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-32530168_ITM|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=Police Special.com|title=Officer Down|url=http://www.policespecial.com/inthelineofduty/2008/K9-Andy/K9-Andy.htm|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120920000854/http://www.policespecial.com/inthelineofduty/2008/K9-Andy/K9-Andy.htm|archivedate=2012-09-20|access-date=2013-04-24}}</ref><ref name=nctc/>，亦為殉職的警犬舉辦隆重的追悼會。<ref name=nctc>{{cite web|publisher=North County Times - Californian|title=Canine commemoration: K-9 Units pay tribute to Stryker, fallen Oceanside police dog|date=2008-01-15|last=Sisson|first=Paul|url=http://www.nctimes.com/articles/2008/01/15/news/coastal/2_01_311_14_08.prt}}{{Dead link|February 2012|date=February 2012}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.roanoke.com/news/nrv/wb/187837 |title=Police dog given an officer's funeral |accessdate=23 December 2008 |last=Moxley |first=Tonia |work= |publisher=The Roanoke Times |date=December 16, 2008 |archive-date=2012-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002151438/http://www.roanoke.com/news/nrv/wb/187837 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|publisher=CTV Canada|title=Nitro the police dog receives a hero's sendoff|date=2006-02-06|url=http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/20060206/nitro_funeral_060206/20060206?hub=Canada|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060818202535/http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/20060206/nitro_funeral_060206/20060206?hub=Canada|archivedate=2006-08-18|accessdate=2013-04-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=警犬殉職 隆重舉殯冚國旗 |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20140830/18850034 |language=中文 |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2014年8月30日 |accessdate=2014年8月30日 |archive-date=2014年9月1日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140901150536/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20140830/18850034 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==歷史==
